; Coverage tests for format.cc lines 361-380 (colorize/ansify_if in format elements)
; Uses --bold-if to trigger the colorize_op code path in format element construction
; Uses --no-color to suppress actual ANSI output so test output matches cleanly

2024/01/01 Payee
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/15 Groceries
    Expenses:Food    $25.00
    Assets:Cash

; This exercises format.cc 361-380: the bold_if format expression gets parsed
; into an ansify_if call wrapping the format element
test reg --bold-if "amount>100" Expenses
24-Jan-01 Payee                 Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
24-Jan-15 Groceries             Expenses:Food                $25.00       $35.00
end test
